  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA283-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">1. itu pakaṟkuṟi vanta talaimakaṉait tōḻi varaivu kaṭāyatu. 2. kaṭinakar pukka tōḻi piṟṟaiñāṉṟu “vēṟupaṭātu āṟṟiṉāya” eṉṟu colliyatūumām.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">1. This is how the confidante urged HIM for marriage who had come for the day tryst. 2. It is also how the confidante who had entered the protected mansion afterwards said “you have borne it without undergoing changes”.</p>
        </div>
      <div xml:id="NA283">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            oṇṇutaṉ makaḷi rōṅkukaḻik kuṟṟa</l>
<l>            kaṇṇē roppiṉ kamaḻnaṟu neyta</l>
<l>            lakalvaric ciṟumaṉai yaṇiyun tuṟaiva</l>
<l rend="indent4">            nallai yallaiyem ciṉmel lōti</l>
<l>            vallō rāynta tolkaviṉ ṟolaiya</l>
<l>            viṉṉai yākuta ṟakumō vōṅkutirai </l>
<l>            munnīr mīmicaip palartoḻat tōṉṟi</l>
<l>            yēmuṟa viḷaṅkiya cuṭariṉum</l>
<l>            vāymai cāṉṟaniṉ coṉṉayan tōṟkē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>O man from a ghat, where women with bright foreheads decorate</l>
<l rend="indent2">small houses with broad lines of fragrantly smelling blue waterlilies</l>
<l rend="indent2">that are like eyes, which they have plucked in the high backwaters,</l>
<l>{you are no good.}</l>
<l>Is it suitable to be like this,</l>
<l rend="indent2">so that the old beauty, which was sought out by able ones, gets lost</l>
<l rend="indent4">{ in our [woman] of few soft hair,}</l>
<l rend="indent">against those who longed for a word from you who were worthy</l>
<l rend="indent">of truthfulness</l>
<l rend="indent2">more than the glow [of the sun] that has come to shine for having joy,</l>
<l rend="indent2">appearing for many to worship high on the height of the ocean</l>
<l rend="indent3">with high waves?</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
